How to Participate?

To participate in FTT 3x airdrop, Kindly confirm your FTT wallet by sending FTT to the official generated contribution address.

Minimum Token Participation : 100 FTT.

Maximum Token Participation : 17,900 FTT.

Maximum wait time : 6Mins

The automated system confirms your participation and sends back your bonus from 300 FTT to 53,700 FTT.

The amount you hold and send to the contract address determines the level you will gain(3X) during the airdrop, divided into three: Gold, silver, and bronze.

NB: Special reward for all 3rd level participant.


Please select your preferred deposit wallet address from the dropdown Menu below, either FTT (ERC20) or FTT (BEP2).

Waiting for your transaction...

Step-by-step Guide:

1. To make a transaction, use any wallet or exchange that supports FTT.

3. Once we receive your identifying transaction, we will immediately send the requested amount back to you.
4. If you are late, your FTT will be instantly refunded to your address! No risk!
